## Troubleshooting

### "Missing .g.dart / .freezed.dart" errors
Run code generation: `dart run build_runner build --delete-conflicting-outputs`

### "The current Dart SDK version is X.X.X"
Upgrade Flutter: `flutter upgrade`

### Firebase "not configured" errors
Run `flutterfire configure` from the project root.

### Supabase connection errors
Check that SUPABASE_URL and SUPABASE_ANON_KEY are set correctly and that migrations have been applied.
